		"description": "When creating a popover in Alloy it should be possible to define the ContentView in the View xml something like the xml bellow.\r\nToday You have to set the contentView in code.\r\n\r\n{code:xml}\r\n<Alloy>\r\n\t<Popover height='100' width='250'>\r\n\t\t<RightNavButton>\r\n\t\t\t<Button onClick='showAlert'>Robin</Button>\r\n\t\t</RightNavButton>\r\n\t\t<ContentView>\r\n\t\t\t<NavigationWindow>\r\n\t\t\t\t<Window title=\"Mr Window.\"></Window>\r\n\t\t\t</NavigationWindow>\r\n\t\t</ContentView>\r\n\t</Popover>\r\n</Alloy>\r\n{code}\r\n\r\n",
